      <title>自疫情爆发以来，美国购房成本上涨 26%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/homeownership-costs-in-the-us-jumped-26-since-pandemic-began</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2020 年以来，美国的购房成本上涨了 26%，因为在整个经济高通胀时期，税收、保险和水电费等费用都大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/homeownership-costs-in-the-us-jumped-26-since-pandemic-began</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
